metadata.name: The Eyes of the Cat
metadata.description:
"The Eyes of the Cat" is my first OPEN EDITION piece, and it's the last piece I've listed on the eth chain in 2022. Thank you for your support and for always being here. <3

"The Eyes of the Cat" is designed with the same algorithm as the -colorless substance- and -corrosive effects- projects and is an "airdrop" for collectors and artists who own any piece from either project. If you have, check your wallet.

6916px X 4732px / JPEG / 59.9 MB

This is an original artwork by Berke Yapa - Istanbul  
2022
